Richard P. Lavin





Chief Executive Officer and President, Commercial Vehicle Group, Inc.
An ITT director effective May 2013, Mr. Lavin has deep manufacturing operations expertise and extensive experience in Asia gained during a 30-year career with Caterpillar, Inc.. He serves on the board of directors for USG Corp. and the U.S. Business Councils for China, India and Korea. Mr. Lavin also is a member of The Conference Board and the Chicago Council of Global Affairs, and serves on Bradley University’s Board of Trustees.







